text: Rasmus Levin Martinsen (born 14 April 1996) is a Norwegian footballer who plays as a right-back for Hinna Fotball. ==Career== He made his league debut as a substitute against Odd in September 2014. After the 2018 season, Viking did not renew Martinsen's contract and thus he left the club.
